        "id": 2675666,
        "name": "Fred C",
        "username": "Fred_C",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b77776/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-07-13T22:07:29.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=2216429&amp;iNote=7786757\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2013 Domaine Ramonet Chassagne-Montrachet 1er Cru Les Chaum\u00e9es</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Chassagne-Montrachet 1er Cru (7/13/2019)</em><br>\nEvery time I drink Ramonet I am surprised by balanced it is. In this difficult vintage this wine is very refined and balanced with a nice crispness and refreshing acidity.  The fruit is nicely balanced with good weight and there is no awkward oak or heat. A wonderful wine with peel and eat shrimp. Can\u2019t ask for more. Did I mention how balanced this was?</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/d/d/ddf81f294ebe6b7a4a3d382a55e6ae4b30906323.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/ddf81f294ebe6b7a4a3d382a55e6ae4b30906323\" title=\"661B4C11-B7D0-4871-A26F-8DC9A0610AE3.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/d/d/ddf81f294ebe6b7a4a3d382a55e6ae4b30906323_2_375x500.jpeg\" alt=\"661B4C11-B7D0-4871-A26F-8DC9A0610AE3.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"vFD7oDeadXkrJMefWy7UM830abx\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/d/d/ddf81f294ebe6b7a4a3d382a55e6ae4b30906323_2_375x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/d/d/ddf81f294ebe6b7a4a3d382a55e6ae4b30906323_2_562x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/d/d/ddf81f294ebe6b7a4a3d382a55e6ae4b30906323_2_750x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"7D705C\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">661B4C11-B7D0-4871-A26F-8DC9A0610AE3.jpeg</span>