        "created_at": "2019-07-14T16:06:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"153388\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"153388\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>never seen this wine!  Awesome.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>They have owned the vineyard for quite a while but only actually got around to planting it relatively recently.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>there is an 09 for sale via wine-searcher so must have been planted 04 or earlier since the first few vintages aren\u2019t sold. Interesting.</p>",
